The <span pulumi-lang-nodejs="`gitlab.getArtifactFile`" pulumi-lang-dotnet="`gitlab.getArtifactFile`" pulumi-lang-go="`getArtifactFile`" pulumi-lang-python="`get_artifact_file`" pulumi-lang-yaml="`gitlab.getArtifactFile`" pulumi-lang-java="`gitlab.getArtifactFile`">`gitlab.getArtifactFile`</span> data source allows downloading a single artifact file from a specific job in the latest successful pipeline for a given reference (branch, tag, or commit).
